Insider Activity


Individual




Andrew A. Juster



Mr. Andrew A. Juster is Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at Simon Property Group, Inc. and Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at Simon Property Group LP.
Mr. Juster was previously employed as Vice President by Melvin Simon & Associates, Inc. and Senior Vice President & Treasurer by Taubman Centers, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from American University and an MBA from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania.



